timeline.bodyText:
Should this method be something that lives in Utility class. Taking in a boolean of whether to move or delete and the name
e.g.
public void moveOrDeleteParsedFile(boolean move, String fileName) {
        if (moved) {
             Utility.moveFileToParsedDir(fileName, "/parsedBalanceFiles/");
         } else {
             Utility.deleteParsedFile(fileName);
         }
}

That way The FileParser classes only have to call

Utility. moveOrDeleteParsedFile(parserProperties.isKeepFiles(), PARSED_DIR)

